    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_51_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_51_01-ktn001.m4a",
      "text": "もしもし、お疲れ様です。……えっ！？　『ミラクル☆\nアイドルバースデー！』のお願い事、通ったんですか？",
      "startTime": 8.8333330989,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_51_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_51_01-ktn002.m4a",
      "text": "嬉しいに決まってます。クリスマスと誕生日が一緒\nだと、お祝いしてもらってばかりですから",
      "startTime": 16.3333330989,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_51_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_51_01-ktn003.m4a",
      "text": "今回は、私が内緒でみんなを喜ばせたいんです\nあ、サプライズですから、情報の取り扱いには――",
      "startTime": 24.6999990026,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-living-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 4533.333059100002,
          "startTime": 29.2333320617
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_51_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_51_01-skr001.m4a",
      "text": "琴乃ちゃーん",
      "startTime": 30.4999977309,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_51_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_51_01-ktn004.m4a",
      "text": "わぁっ！？\nす、すみませんっ、それでは失礼します！",
      "startTime": 33.2999967137,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-tap-01.m4a",
          "delay": 4590.000000000004,
          "startTime": 37.123330047
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_51_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_51_01-skr002.m4a",
      "text": "あっ、ごめんね。電話してたんだ",
      "startTime": 38.0999967137,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_51_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_51_01-ktn005.m4a",
      "text": "だ、大丈夫。もう切るとこだったから\n{user}さんと仕事の話をしてたの",
      "startTime": 46.2666633803,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_51_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_51_01-skr003.m4a",
      "text": "もしかして\n『ミラクル☆アイドルバースデー！』のこと？\nもうすぐお誕生日だもんね～。何をお願いするの？",
      "startTime": 53.9666666864,
      "sfxList": []
    }
  ]
}